    <abstract id="aspace_ffbfeb3c8aad636bc93d118ed6cae859">Charles A. Bill was an illustrator who contributed to the 1891-1892 volume of the <emph render = "italic">Violet</emph>, New York University's yearbook. This collection contains sketches and drawings by Bill that were published in the <emph render = "italic">Violet</emph>.  Cartoons found within this collection depict NYU clubs, athletics group, and student societies. There is also one drawing of an angel.</abstract>
    <physloc id="aspace_a07376fabbab36ce41e0572e0ecd442a">Materials are stored offsite and advance notice is required for use. Please request materials at least two business days prior to your research visit to coordinate access.</physloc>
    <langmaterial id="aspace_27606471a27cda4695eee191faed5118">The materials are in English.</langmaterial>
  </did>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_2f6897ff8dce864b79d14ceaf05896e4">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>This collection contains sketches and drawings by Charles A. Bill that were published in the 1891-1892 volume of the <emph render = "italic">Violet</emph>. Cartoons found within this collection depict NYU clubs, athletics group, and student societies. There is also one drawing of an angel.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <arrangement id="aspace_11059d2856e3a637ce85787cc9ad02fb">
    <head>Arrangement</head>
<p>This collection has not been arranged by an archivist. The materials are arranged in the order in which they were received.</p>  </arrangement>
  <acqinfo id="aspace_f5d7c99d4aee8d8062e5104306f6dce2">
    <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
<p>Material in this collection was transferred from the New York University Archives Photograph Collection (PHOTO 00001) in May 2024. The accession number associated with this collection is 2024.041.</p>  </acqinfo>
  <accessrestrict id="aspace_95eb2c1372dcc4dc1b5de4269657479a">
    <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
<p>Materials are open without restrictions.</p>  </accessrestrict>
  <userestrict id="aspace_5ee658dce10862d8b07f2348798b9ea1">
    <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
<p>This collection is protected by copyright and/or related rights. You are free to use materials in the collection in any way that is permitted by the copyright and related rights legislation that applies to your use. For other uses you need to obtain permission from the rights-holder(s).</p>  </userestrict>
  <bioghist id="aspace_090de0a407a9f9fd1e21f07e34d1b445">
    <head>Biographical Note</head>
<p>Charles A. Bill was born in 1871. His death date is unknown. He contributed to the 1891-1892 volume of the <emph render = "italic">Violet</emph>.</p>  </bioghist>
  <prefercite id="aspace_9b94e2568c77c7864c7ee6592e642c01">
    <head>Preferred Citation</head>
<p>Identification of item, date; Charles A. Bill Collection; MC 402; box number; folder number or item identifier; New York University Archives, New York University</p>  </prefercite>
  <processinfo id="aspace_1376f084552bfb399f2cda45e38dad95">
    <head>Processing Information</head>
<p>In May 2024, Charles A. Bill's cartoons and drawings were removed from the New York University Archives Photograph Collection (PHOTO 00001) and transferred to MC 402. Materials were rehoused in acid-free boxes and folders. Original titles were retained. Materials were described on the collection-level and inventoried at the box-level.</p>  </processinfo>
